title: Zootopia (2016)
description:
Hello, included here is the Original Motion Picture Sountrack/Original Score for the movie Zootopia. Composed by Michael Giacchino.

It includes the single "Try Everything" from Shakira. 

  
https://play.google.com/store/music/album/Michael_Giacchino_Zootopia_Original_Motion_Picture?id=B4ivch2ewmltohplrndzl36p2ui&hl=en

There are 22 tracks in total.
